title: Paquito d'Rivera on Franisco Yobino & the Uruguay Jazz Festival
description:
In this interview done during the Jazz Cruise in 2016, saxophonist and clarinetist Paquito D’Rivera talks about the Festival Internacional de Jazz de Punta del Este in Uruguay and its artistic director, Francisco Yobino. D'Rivera has been the artistic director for the festival for several years. D’Rivera was performing on the cruise with his sextet.

Interview by Irene Lee.  Video production by Lee Mergner & Melissa Mergner. Thanks to Michael Lazaroff and the production team of Entertainment Cruise Productions. 

For more information about Paquito D’Rivera, go to www.paquitodrivera.com

For more information about the Jazz Cruise, go to www.thejazzcruise.com

For more information about JazzTimes, go to www.jazztimes.com
